Manufacturer: Wacom
Model Name: One pen tablet Small
Model Number: CTC4110WL

Notes:

Uses Wacom's alternate 0x0531 vendor ID. This data is captured from the 
tablet in its standard "PC Mode", which presents a different PID  
and HID descriptor compared to the alternate "Android Mode".

USB:0531:0100

